	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Petruza wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Please explain further.<br />Colors? you mean use them as actual palette indexes?</div>
<br />If the VRAM address register is pointing to the palette area while rendering is disabled, the color being pointed is shown on the screen, rather than color 0.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


